600090,122,4722,72,86,1,56,11,"Yena ca te attho hoti, sabbaṃ mama santikā gaṇhāhī’’ ti āha. "
600091,122,4722,87,94,1,61,7,Nirodhā vuṭṭhitassa pana dinnapiṇḍapāto tadaheva vipākaṃ deti. 
