600093,122,4723,2,29,1,226,25,"So sumanaseṭṭhissa sahāyako hutvā yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā tato cuto devaloke nibbattitvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kapilavatthunagare amitodanassa sakkassa gehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi, anuruddho tissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
