600336,122,4803,88,126,1,227,28,"Atha naṃ satthā,‘‘ ānanda, sūriyo nāma divā virocati, cando rattiṃ, rājā alaṅkatakāleyeva, khīṇāsave gaṇasaṅgaṇikaṃ pahāya antosamāpattiyaṃyeva virocati, buddhā pana rattimpi divāpi pañcavidhena tejena virocantī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
