600350,122,4813,2,36,1,199,25,"Eko kira brāhmaṇo bāhirakapabbajjāya pabbajitvā‘‘ samaṇo gotamo attano sāvake‘ pabbajitā’ ti vadati, ahañcamhi pabbajito, mampi kho evaṃ vattuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ pucchi. "
600351,122,4813,37,60,1,117,16,"Satthā‘‘ nāhaṃ ettakena‘ pabbajito’ ti vadāmi, kilesamalānaṃ pana pabbājitattā pabbajito nāma hotī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
600352,122,4814,2,4,1,0,0,388.
600353,122,4815,2,10,1,49,6,"‘ ‘ Bāhitapāpoti brāhmaṇo, samacariyā samaṇoti vuccati; "
600354,122,4816,2,11,1,51,6,"Pabbājayamattano malaṃ, tasmā pabbajitoti vuccatī’’ ti. "
600355,122,4817,2,8,1,50,5,Tattha {samacariyā}ti sabbākusalāni sametvā caraṇena. 
600356,122,4817,9,35,1,189,22,"{Tasmā}ti yasmā bāhitapāpatāya brāhmaṇo, akusalāni sametvā caraṇena samaṇoti vuccati, tasmā yo attano rāgādimalaṃ pabbājayanto vinodento carati, sopi tena pabbājanena pabbajitoti vuccatīti attho. "
600357,122,4818,2,12,1,103,9,"Desanāvasāne so brāhmaṇapabbajito sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi, sampattānampi sātthikā dhammadesanā ahosīti. "
