600368,122,4822,94,113,1,127,14,"So‘‘ hotu, jānissāmissa kattabban’’ ti theraṃ bhikkhāya paviṭṭhaṃ disvā pacchābhāgena gantvā piṭṭhimajjhe mahantaṃ pāṇippahāramadāsi. "
600369,122,4822,114,124,1,38,6,Thero‘‘ kiṃ nāmetan’’ ti anoloketvāva gato. 
