600371,122,4822,130,172,1,147,24,"So‘‘ aho guṇasampanno, ayyo’’ ti therassa pādamūle nipajjitvā‘‘ khamatha me, bhante’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kiṃ etan’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ ahaṃ vīmaṃsanatthāya tumhe paharin’’ ti āha."
600372,122,4822,173,181,1,18,4,‘‘ Hotu khamāmi te’’ ti.
600373,122,4822,182,206,1,111,16,"‘‘ Sace me, bhante, khamatha, mama geheyeva nisīditvā bhikkhaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti therassa pattaṃ gaṇhi, theropi pattaṃ adāsi. "
600374,122,4822,207,212,1,36,5,Brāhmaṇo theraṃ gehaṃ netvā parivisi. 
