600378,122,4823,56,59,1,18,3,Kiṃ etaṃ upāsakāti? 
600379,122,4823,60,68,1,55,6,"Brāhmaṇena tumhe pahaṭā, mayamassa kattabbaṃ jānissāmāti. "
