600408,122,4836,30,52,1,159,17,"Evaṃ laddhūpasampadaṃ theriṃ ārabbha aparena samayena kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ mahāpajāpatiyā gotamiyā ācariyupajjhāyā na paññāyanti, sahattheneva kāsāyāni gaṇhī’’ ti. "
