600990,122,5105,2,15,1,98,12,Tatrāyaṃ anupubbī kathā– atīte kira bārāṇasiyaṃ dve bhātaro kuṭumbikā mahantaṃ ucchukhettaṃ kāresuṃ. 
600991,122,5105,16,39,1,176,18,"Athekadivasaṃ kaniṭṭhabhātā ucchukhettaṃ gantvā‘‘ ekaṃ jeṭṭhabhātikassa dassāmi, ekaṃ mayhaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti dve ucchuyaṭṭhiyo rasassa anikkhamanatthāya chinnaṭṭhāne bandhitvā gaṇhi. "
600992,122,5105,40,59,1,137,18,"Tadā kira ucchūnaṃ yantena pīḷanakiccaṃ natthi, agge vā mūle vā chinditvā ukkhittakāle dhammakaraṇato udakaṃ viya sayameva raso nikkhamati. "
600993,122,5105,60,99,1,284,34,Tassa pana khettato ucchuyaṭṭhiyo gahetvā āgamanakāle gandhamādane paccekabuddho samāpattito vuṭṭhāya‘‘ kassa nu kho ajja anuggahaṃ karissāmī’’ ti upadhārento taṃ attano ñāṇajāle paviṭṭhaṃ disvā saṅgahaṃ kātuṃ samatthabhāvañca ñatvā pattacīvaraṃ ādāya iddhiyā āgantvā tassa purato aṭṭhāsi. 
600994,122,5105,100,138,1,233,27,"So taṃ disvāva pasannacitto uttarasāṭakaṃ uccatare bhūmipadese attharitvā,‘‘ bhante, idha nisīdathā’’ ti paccekabuddhaṃ nisīdāpetvā‘‘ pattaṃ upanāmethā’’ ti ucchuyaṭṭhiyā bandhanaṭṭhānaṃ mocetvā pattassa upari akāsi, raso otaritvā pattaṃ pūresi. "
600995,122,5105,139,151,1,66,10,Paccekabuddhena tasmiṃ rase pīte‘‘ sādhukaṃ vata me ayyena raso pīto. 
600996,122,5105,152,160,1,54,7,"Sace me jeṭṭhabhātiko mūlaṃ āharāpessati, mūlaṃ dassāmi. "
600997,122,5105,161,187,1,125,17,"Sace pattiṃ āharāpessati, pattiṃ dassāmī’’ ti cintetvā,‘‘ bhante, pattaṃ me upanāmethā’’ ti dutiyampi ucchuyaṭṭhiṃ mocetvā rasaṃ adāsi."
600998,122,5105,188,204,1,97,12,‘‘ Bhātā me ucchukhettato aññaṃ ucchuṃ āharitvā khādissatī’’ ti ettakampi kirassa vañcanacittaṃ nāhosi. 
600999,122,5105,205,220,1,120,13,Paccekabuddho pana paṭhamaṃ ucchurasassa pītattā taṃ ucchurasaṃ aññehipi saddhiṃ saṃvibhajitukāmo hutvā gahetvāva nisīdi . 
601000,122,5105,221,252,1,207,24,"So tassa ākāraṃ ñatvā pañcapatiṭṭhitena vanditvā,‘‘ bhante, yo ayaṃ mayā dinno aggaraso, imassa nissandena devamanussesu sampattiṃ anubhavitvā pariyosāne tumhehi pattadhammameva pāpuṇeyyan’’ ti patthanaṃ paṭṭhapesi. "
601001,122,5105,253,289,1,209,26,"Paccekabuddhopissa‘‘ evaṃ hotū’’ ti vatvā‘‘ icchitaṃ patthitaṃ tuyhan’’ ti dvīhi gāthāhi anumodanaṃ katvā yathā so passati, evaṃ adhiṭṭhahitvā ākāsena gandhamādanaṃ gantvā pañcannaṃ paccekabuddhasatānaṃ taṃ rasaṃ adāsi. "
601002,122,5106,2,25,1,101,15,So taṃ pāṭihāriyaṃ disvā bhātu santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ kahaṃ gatosī’’ ti vutte‘‘ ucchukhettaṃ oloketuṃ gatomhī’’ ti.
601003,122,5106,26,48,1,114,17,"‘‘ Kiṃ tādisena ucchukhettaṃ gatena, nanu nāma ekaṃ vā dve vā ucchuyaṭṭhiyo ādāya āgantabbaṃ bhaveyyā’’ ti bhātarā vutto–"
601004,122,5106,49,95,1,225,35,"‘‘ āma, bhātika, dve me ucchuyaṭṭhiyo gahitā, ekaṃ pana paccekabuddhaṃ disvā mama ucchuyaṭṭhito rasaṃ datvā‘ mūlaṃ vā pattiṃ vā dassāmī’ ti tumhākampi me ucchuyaṭṭhito raso dinno, kiṃ nu kho tassa mūlaṃ gaṇhissatha, udāhu pattin’’ ti āha."
601005,122,5106,96,105,1,33,5,‘‘ Kiṃ pana paccekabuddhena katan’’ ti?
601006,122,5106,106,125,1,135,15,‘‘ Mama ucchuyaṭṭhito rasaṃ pivitvā tumhākaṃ ucchuyaṭṭhito rasaṃ ādāya ākāsena gandhamādanaṃ gantvā pañcasatānaṃ paccekabuddhānaṃ adāsī’’ ti. 
601007,122,5106,126,146,1,139,16,So tasmiṃ kathenteyeva nirantaraṃ pītiyā phuṭṭhasarīro hutvā‘‘ tena me paccekabuddhena diṭṭhadhammasseva adhigamo bhaveyyā’’ ti patthanaṃ akāsi. 
601008,122,5106,147,161,1,112,13,"Evaṃ kaniṭṭhena tisso sampattiyo patthitā, jeṭṭhena pana ekapadeneva arahattaṃ patthitanti idaṃ tesaṃ pubbakammaṃ. "
601009,122,5107,2,12,1,81,10,Te yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cutā devaloke nibbattitvā ekaṃ buddhantaraṃ khepayiṃsu. 
601010,122,5107,13,20,1,64,7,Tesaṃ devaloke ṭhitakāleyeva vipassī sammāsambuddho loke uppajji. 
601011,122,5107,21,35,1,116,13,"Tepi devalokato cavitvā bandhumatiyā ekasmiṃ kulagehe jeṭṭho jeṭṭhova, kaniṭṭho kaniṭṭhova hutvā paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhiṃsu. "
