601021,122,5108,70,74,1,34,4,Ahaṃ satthu santike pabbajissāmīti. 
601022,122,5108,75,105,1,164,25,"Sāmi kiṃ vadetha, ahaṃ mātari matāya mātaraṃ viya, pitari mate pitaraṃ viya tumhe alatthaṃ, idaṃ kulaṃ mahābhogaṃ, gehe ṭhiteneva sakkā puññāni kātuṃ, mā evaṃ karitthāti. "
