601027,122,5108,186,203,1,67,11,"Atha naṃ thero‘‘ sādhu sādhu, paṇḍita, satthu gandhakuṭiṃ karohī’’ ti āha. "
601028,122,5108,204,234,1,253,24,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā nānādārūni āharāpetvā thambhādīnaṃ atthāya tacchāpetvā ekaṃ suvaṇṇakhacitaṃ, ekaṃ rajatakhacitaṃ, ekaṃ maṇikhacitanti sabbāni sattaratanakhacitāni kāretvā tehi gandhakuṭiṃ kāretvā sattaratanakhacitāheva chadaniṭṭhakāhi chādāpesi. "
601029,122,5108,235,258,1,153,18,"Gandhakuṭiyā karaṇakāleyeva pana taṃ attanā samānanāmako aparājitoyeva nāma bhāgineyyo upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ ahampi karissāmi, mayhampi pattiṃ detha mātulā’’ ti āha. "
601030,122,5108,259,267,1,43,6,"Na demi, tāta, aññehi asādhāraṇaṃ karissāmīti. "
601031,122,5108,268,286,1,125,14,So bahumpi yācitvā pattiṃ alabhamāno‘‘ gandhakuṭiyā purato kuñjarasālaṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti sattaratanamayaṃ kuñjarasālaṃ kāresi. 
601032,122,5108,287,293,1,51,6,So imasmiṃ buddhuppāde meṇḍakaseṭṭhi hutvā nibbatti. 
601033,122,5109,2,9,1,63,6,Gandhakuṭiyaṃ pana sattaratanamayāni tīṇi mahāvātapānāni ahesuṃ. 
601034,122,5109,10,34,1,240,22,"Tesaṃ abhimukhe heṭṭhā sudhāparikammakatā tisso pokkharaṇiyo kāretvā catujjātikagandhodakassa pūretvā aparājito, gahapati, pañcavaṇṇāni kusumāni ropāpesi tathāgatassa anto nisinnakāle vātavegena samuṭṭhitāhi reṇuvaṭṭīhi sarīrassa okiraṇatthaṃ. "
601035,122,5109,35,46,1,101,9,"Gandhakuṭithūpikāya kapallaṃ rattasuvaṇṇamayaṃ ahosi, pavāḷamayā sikharā, heṭṭhā maṇimayā chadaniṭṭhakā. "
601036,122,5109,47,54,1,43,7,Iti sā naccanto viya moro sobhamānā aṭṭhāsi. 
601037,122,5109,55,70,1,138,14,Sattasu pana ratanesu koṭṭetabbayuttakaṃ koṭṭetvā itaraṃ sakalameva gahetvā jaṇṇumattena odhinā gandhakuṭiṃ parikkhipitvā pariveṇaṃ pūresi. 
601038,122,5110,2,12,1,80,8,"Evaṃ gandhakuṭiṃ niṭṭhāpetvā aparājito, gahapati, bhātikattheraṃ upasaṅkamitvā āha–"
601039,122,5110,13,32,1,94,11,"‘‘ bhante, niṭṭhitā gandhakuṭi, paribhogamassā paccāsīsāmi, paribhogena kira mahantaṃ puññaṃ hotī’’ ti . "
601040,122,5110,33,56,1,118,16,"So satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā,‘‘ bhante, iminā kira vo kuṭumbikena gandhakuṭi kāritā, idāni pana paribhogaṃ paccāsīsatī’’ ti āha. "
601041,122,5110,57,67,1,126,10,Satthā uṭṭhāyāsanā gandhakuṭiabhimukhaṃ gantvā gandhakuṭiṃ parikkhipitvā parikkhittaratanarāsiṃ olokento dvārakoṭṭhake aṭṭhāsi. 
