601046,122,5110,117,153,1,218,28,"So tassa vacanaṃ sutvā satthāraṃ pañcapatiṭṭhitena vanditvā,‘‘ bhante, yathā manussā rukkhamūle pavisitvā anapekkhā pakkamanti, yathā vā nadiṃ taritvā uḷumpaṃ anapekkhā pariccajanti, evaṃ anapekkhā hutvā tumhe vasathā’’ ti āha. "
