601259,122,5127,157,168,1,79,10,Iti so putte anusāsitvā satthu santike pabbajitvā katipāheneva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
601260,122,5127,169,188,1,172,18,"Satthā aparena samayena pañcahi bhikkhusatehi saddhiṃ piṇḍāya caranto tassa puttānaṃ gehadvāraṃ agamāsi, te buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa aḍḍhamāsaṃ bhikkhādānaṃ adaṃsu. "
601261,122,5128,2,25,1,122,16,"Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ ajjāpi te, āvuso jaṭila, asītihatthe suvaṇṇapabbate ca puttesu ca taṇhā atthī’’ ti."
