601290,122,5138,172,206,1,145,23,"Atha naṃ seṭṭhi‘‘ evaṃ, deva, mama santakaṃ mama anicchāya na sakkā gaṇhitun’’ ti vatvā rañño kiriyāya uppannasaṃvego‘‘ pabbajituṃ me anujāna, devā’’ ti āha. "
