601821,123,129,23,40,1,93,12,Atha vā teyeva ‘‘ veneyyasattasantānesu kathaṃ nu kho uppajjeyyun’’ ti vani abhipatthayīti bhagavā. 
601822,123,129,41,53,1,98,12,Atha vā bhagasaṅkhātaṃ issariyaṃ yasañca vami uggiri kheḷapiṇḍaṃ viya anapekkho chaḍḍayīti bhagavā. 
601823,123,129,54,79,1,272,23,"Tathā hi tathāgato hatthagataṃ cakkavattisiriṃ devalokādhipaccasadisaṃ cātuddīpissariyaṃ, cakkavattisampattisannissayañca sattaratanasamujjalaṃ yasaṃ tiṇāyapi amaññamāno nirapekkho pahāya abhinikkhamitvā sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho, tasmā ime siriādike bhage vamīti bhagavā. "
