601896,123,144,25,40,1,112,13,"Attano ajjhāsayo attajjhāsayo, so assa atthi kāraṇabhūtoti attajjhāsayo, attano ajjhāsayo etassāti vā attajjhāsayo. "
601897,123,144,41,44,1,25,3,Parajjhāsayepi eseva nayo. 
601898,123,144,45,53,1,55,7,"Pucchāya vaso pucchāvaso, so etassa atthīti pucchāvasiko. "
601899,123,144,54,68,1,117,12,"Suttadesanāya vatthubhūtassa atthassa uppatti atthuppatti, atthuppatti eva aṭṭhuppatti, sā etassa atthīti aṭṭhuppattiko. "
601900,123,144,69,78,1,63,8,"Atha vā nikkhipīyati suttaṃ etenāti nikkhepo, attajjhāsayādi eva. "
