602234,123,206,2,4,1,20,2,4 . Huṃhuṅkasuttavaṇṇanā 
602235,123,207,2,25,1,115,13,"4. Catutthe {ajapālanigrodhe}ti tassa kira chāyāyaṃ ajapālā gantvā nisīdanti, tenassa‘‘ ajapālanigrodho’’ tveva nāmaṃ udapādi. "
602236,123,207,26,51,1,169,19,"Keci pana‘‘ yasmā tattha vede sajjhāyituṃ asamatthā mahallakabrāhmaṇā pākāraparikkhepayuttāni nivesanāni katvā sabbe vasiṃsu, tasmā {ajapālanigrodho}ti nāmaṃ jātan’’ ti vadanti. "
602237,123,207,52,69,1,114,14,"Tatrāyaṃ vacanattho– na japantīti ajapā, mantānaṃ anajjhāyakāti attho, ajapā lanti ādiyanti nivāsaṃ etthāti ajapāloti. "
602238,123,207,70,90,1,117,17,"Yasmā vā majjhanhike samaye anto paviṭṭhe aje attano chāyāya pāleti rakkhati, tasmā‘ ajapālo’ tissa nāmaṃ rūḷhanti apare. "
602239,123,207,91,98,1,49,6,"Sabbathāpi nāmametaṃ tassa rukkhassa, tassa samīpe. "
602240,123,207,99,109,1,45,6,Samīpatthe hi etaṃ bhummaṃ‘‘ ajapālanigrodhe’’ ti. 
602241,123,208,2,10,1,89,7,{Vimuttisukhapaṭisaṃvedī}ti tatrapi dhammaṃ vicinanto vimuttisukhañca paṭisaṃvedento nisīdi. 
602242,123,208,11,16,1,49,5,Bodhirukkhato puratthimadisābhāge esa rukkho hoti. 
602243,123,208,17,24,1,57,7,Sattāhan ti ca idaṃ na pallaṅkasattāhato anantarasattāhaṃ. 
602244,123,208,25,33,1,80,8,Bhagavā hi pallaṅkasattāhato aparānipi tīṇi sattāhāni bodhisamīpeyeva vītināmesi. 
602245,123,209,2,32,1,191,23,"Tatrāyaṃ anupubbikathā– bhagavati kira sammāsambodhiṃ patvā sattāhaṃ ekapallaṅkena nisinne‘‘ na bhagavā vuṭṭhāti, kinnu kho aññepi buddhattakarā dhammā atthī’’ ti ekaccānaṃ devatānaṃ kaṅkhā udapādi. "
602246,123,209,33,74,1,411,40,"Atha bhagavā aṭṭhame divase samāpattito vuṭṭhāya devatānaṃ kaṅkhaṃ ñatvā kaṅkhāvidhamanatthaṃ ākāse uppatitvā yamakapāṭihāriyaṃ dassetvā tāsaṃ kaṅkhaṃ vidhametvā pallaṅkato īsakaṃ pācīnanissite uttaradisābhāge ṭhatvā cattāri asaṅkhyeyyāni kappasatasahassañca upacitānaṃ pāramīnaṃ balādhigamaṭṭhānaṃ pallaṅkaṃ bodhirukkhañca animisehi cakkhūhi olokayamāno sattāhaṃ vītināmesi, taṃ ṭhānaṃ animisacetiyaṃ nāma jātaṃ. "
602247,123,209,75,96,1,161,19,"Atha pallaṅkassa ca ṭhitaṭṭhānassa ca antarā puratthimato ca pacchimato ca āyate ratanacaṅkame caṅkamanto sattāhaṃ vītināmesi, taṃ ratanacaṅkamacetiyaṃ nāma jātaṃ. "
602248,123,209,97,120,1,207,20,"Tato pacchimadisābhāge devatā ratanagharaṃ māpayiṃsu , tattha pallaṅkena nisīditvā abhidhammapiṭakaṃ visesato anantanayaṃ samantapaṭṭhānaṃ vicinanto sattāhaṃ vītināmesi, taṃ ṭhānaṃ ratanagharacetiyaṃ nāma jātaṃ. "
602249,123,209,121,135,1,140,14,Evaṃ bodhisamīpeyeva cattāri sattāhāni vītināmetvā pañcame sattāhe bodhirukkhato ajapālanigrodhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tassa mūle pallaṅkena nisīdi. 
602250,123,210,2,24,1,174,20,"Tamhā samādhimhā {vuṭṭhāsī}ti tato phalasamāpattisamādhito yathākālaparicchedaṃ vuṭṭhahi, vuṭṭhahitvā ca pana tattha evaṃ nisinne bhagavati eko brāhmaṇo taṃ gantvā pañhaṃ pucchi. "
