602434,123,242,146,156,1,92,9,"Sāre patiṭṭhitan ti vimuttisāre avaṭṭhitaṃ, asekkhasīlakkhandhādike vā sīlādisāre patiṭṭhitaṃ. "
602435,123,242,157,166,1,88,9,Khīṇāsavaṃ vantadosan ti kāmāsavādīnaṃ catunnaṃ āsavānaṃ anavasesaṃ pahīnattā khīṇāsavaṃ. 
