602440,123,244,2,4,1,23,2,7 . Ajakalāpakasuttavaṇṇanā 
602441,123,245,2,11,1,49,6,7. Sattame pāvāyan ti evaṃnāmake mallarājūnaṃ nagare. 
602442,123,245,12,30,1,117,11,Ajakalāpake {cetiye}ti ajakalāpakena nāma yakkhena pariggahitattā‘‘ ajakalāpakan’’ ti laddhanāme manussānaṃ cittīkataṭṭhāne . 
602443,123,245,31,54,1,125,17,"So kira yakkho aje kalāpe katvā bandhanena ajakoṭṭhāsena saddhiṃ baliṃ paṭicchati, na aññathā, tasmā‘‘ ajakalāpako’’ ti paññāyittha. "
602444,123,245,55,63,1,51,7,Keci panāhu– ajake viya satte lāpetīti ajakalāpakoti. 
602445,123,245,64,87,1,116,17,"Tassa kira sattā baliṃ upanetvā yadā ajasaddaṃ katvā baliṃ upaharanti, tadā so tussati, tasmā‘‘ ajakalāpako’’ ti vuccatīti. "
602446,123,245,88,109,1,138,19,"So pana yakkho ānubhāvasampanno kakkhaḷo pharuso tattha ca sannihito, tasmā taṃ ṭhānaṃ manussā cittiṃ karonti, kālena kālaṃ baliṃ upaharanti. "
602447,123,245,110,119,1,33,5,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ ajakalāpake cetiye’’ ti. 
602448,123,245,120,127,1,57,6,Ajakalāpakassa yakkhassa {bhavane}ti tassa yakkhassa vimāne. 
602449,123,246,2,21,1,173,19,Tadā kira satthā taṃ yakkhaṃ dametukāmo sāyanhasamaye eko adutiyo pattacīvaraṃ ādāya ajakalāpakassa yakkhassa bhavanadvāraṃ gantvā tassa dovārikaṃ bhavanapavisanatthāya yāci. 
602450,123,246,22,62,1,223,30,"So‘‘ kakkhaḷo, bhante, ajakalāpako yakkho, samaṇoti vā brāhmaṇoti vā gāravaṃ na karoti, tasmā tumhe eva jānātha, mayhaṃ pana tassa anārocanaṃ na yuttan’’ ti tāvadeva yakkhasamāgamaṃ gatassa ajakalāpakassa santikaṃ vātavegena agamāsi. "
602451,123,246,63,70,1,80,7,Satthā antobhavanaṃ pavisitvā ajakalāpakassa nisīdanamaṇḍape paññattāsane nisīdi. 
602452,123,246,71,78,1,68,7,Yakkhassa orodhā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. 
602453,123,246,79,85,1,46,6,Satthā tāsaṃ kālayuttaṃ dhammiṃ kathaṃ kathesi. 
602454,123,246,86,88,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
602455,123,246,89,101,1,71,8,‘‘ pāvāyaṃ viharati ajakalāpake cetiye ajakalāpakassa yakkhassa bhavane’’ ti. 
602456,123,247,2,79,1,509,57,"Tasmiṃ samaye sātāgirahemavatā ajakalāpakassa bhavanamatthakena yakkhasamāgamaṃ gacchantā attano gamane asampajjamāne‘‘ kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti āvajjentā satthāraṃ ajakalāpakassa bhavane nisinnaṃ disvā tattha gantvā bhagavantaṃ vanditvā‘‘ mayaṃ, bhante, yakkhasamāgamaṃ gamissāmā’’ ti āpucchitvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā gatā yakkhasannipāte ajakalāpakaṃ disvā tuṭṭhiṃ pavedayiṃsu‘‘ lābhā te, āvuso, ajakalāpaka, yassa te bhavane sadevake loke aggapuggalo bhagavā nisinno, upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ payirupāsassu, dhammañca suṇāhī’’ ti. "
602457,123,247,80,125,1,300,36,"So tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ ime tassa muṇḍakassa samaṇakassa mama bhavane nisinnabhāvaṃ kathentī’’ ti kodhābhibhūto hutvā‘‘ ajja mayhaṃ tena samaṇena saddhiṃ saṅgāmo bhavissatī’’ ti cintetvā yakkhasannipātato uṭṭhahitvā dakkhiṇaṃ pādaṃ ukkhipitvā saṭṭhiyojanamattaṃ pabbatakūṭaṃ akkami, taṃ bhijjitvā dvidhā ahosi. "
602458,123,247,126,148,1,77,8,"Sesaṃ ettha yaṃ vattabbaṃ, taṃ āḷavakasuttavaṇṇanāyaṃ( saṃ. ni. aṭṭha.1.1.246) āgatanayeneva veditabbaṃ. "
602459,123,248,2,14,1,129,11,Ajakalāpakassa samāgamo hi āḷavakasamāgamasadisova ṭhapetvā pañhakaraṇaṃ vissajjanaṃ bhavanato tikkhattuṃ nikkhamanaṃ pavesanañca. 
602460,123,248,15,57,1,394,38,Ajakalāpako hi āgacchantoyeva‘‘ etehiyeva taṃ samaṇaṃ palāpessāmī’’ ti vātamaṇḍalādike navavasse samuṭṭhāpetvā tehi bhagavato calanamattampi kātuṃ asakkonto nānāvidhappaharaṇahatthe ativiya bhayānakarūpe bhūtagaṇe nimminitvā tehi saddhiṃ bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā antanteneva caranto sabbarattiṃ nānappakāraṃ vippakāraṃ katvāpi bhagavato kiñci kesaggamattampi nisinnaṭṭhānato calanaṃ kātuṃ nāsakkhi. 
602461,123,248,58,75,1,96,13,Kevalaṃ pana‘‘ ayaṃ samaṇo maṃ anāpucchā mayhaṃ bhavanaṃ pavisitvā nisīdatī’’ ti kodhavasena pajjali. 
602462,123,248,76,116,1,267,32,"Athassa bhagavā cittappavattiṃ ñatvā‘‘ seyyathāpi nāma caṇḍassa kukkurassa nāsāya pittaṃ bhindeyya, evaṃ so bhiyyosomattāya caṇḍataro assa, evamevāyaṃ yakkho mayi idha nisinne cittaṃ padūseti, yaṃnūnāhaṃ bahi nikkhameyyan’’ ti sayameva bhavanato nikkhamitvā abbhokāse nisīdi. "
