604431,123,735,2,17,1,82,9,"26. Chaṭṭhe {pilindavaccho}ti pilindā tissa nāmaṃ, {vaccho}ti gottavasena theraṃ sañjānanti. "
604432,123,735,18,37,1,98,11,"Vasalavādena {samudācaratī}ti‘‘ ehi, vasala, apehi, vasalā’’ tiādinā bhikkhū vasalavādena voharati ālapati. "
604433,123,735,38,43,1,32,4,Sambahulā {bhikkhū}ti bahū bhikkhū. 
604434,123,735,44,79,1,208,26,Te theraṃ tathā samudācarantaṃ disvā‘‘ arahāva samāno appahīnavāsanattā evaṃ bhaṇatī’’ ti ajānantā‘‘ dosantaro maññe ayaṃ thero evaṃ samudācaratī’’ ti cintetvā ullapanādhippāyā taṃ tato vuṭṭhāpetuṃ bhagavato ārocesuṃ. 
604435,123,735,80,83,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
604436,123,735,84,97,1,64,7,"‘‘ āyasmā, bhante, pilindavaccho bhikkhū vasalavādena samudācaratī’’ ti. "
604437,123,735,98,100,1,11,2,Keci panāhu–
604438,123,735,101,141,1,259,30,"‘‘ imaṃ theraṃ bhikkhū‘ arahā’ ti sañjānanti, ayañca bhikkhū pharusavacanena evaṃ samudācarati,‘ abhūto eva nu kho imasmiṃ uttarimanussadhammo’ ti vāsanāvasena tassa tathā samudācāraṃ ajānantā ariyabhāvañcassa asaddahantā ujjhānasaññino bhagavato tamatthaṃ ārocesun’’ ti. "
604439,123,735,142,165,1,164,17,"Bhagavā therassa dosantarābhāvaṃ pakāsetukāmo ekena bhikkhunā taṃ pakkosāpetvā sammukhā tassa‘‘ pubbāciṇṇavasenāyaṃ tathā samudācarati, na pharusavacanādhippāyo’’ ti āha. "
