604895,123,837,2,34,1,307,28,"Ayaṃ paṭhamo dhammo paripākāya {saṃvattatī}ti, ayaṃ kalyāṇamittatāsaṅkhāto brahmacariyavāsassa ādibhāvato, sabbesañca kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ bahukāratāya padhānabhāvato ca imesu pañcasu dhammesu ādito vuttattā paṭhamo anavajjadhammo avisuddhānaṃ saddhādīnaṃ visuddhikaraṇavasena cetovimuttiyā paripākāya saṃvattati. "
