604940,123,844,24,40,1,120,14,"Sabbaguṇānaṃ vā tammūlabhāvato uttamaṭṭhena pati ca, so yathāvuttaṭṭhena mokkho cāti patimokkho, patimokkho eva pātimokkho. "
