604942,123,845,2,18,1,93,13,"Atha vā pa iti pakāre, {atī}ti accantatthe nipāto, tasmā pakārehi accantaṃ mokkhetīti pātimokkhaṃ. "
604943,123,845,19,33,1,140,13,"Idañhi sīlaṃ sayaṃ tadaṅgavasena, samādhisahitaṃ paññāsahitañca vikkhambhanavasena samucchedavasena ca accantaṃ mokkheti mocetīti pātimokkhaṃ. "
604944,123,845,34,45,1,79,10,"Pati mokkhoti vā patimokkho, tamhā tamhā vītikkamadosato paccekaṃ mokkhoti attho. "
604945,123,845,46,50,1,25,3,Patimokkho eva pātimokkho. 
604946,123,845,51,59,1,64,7,"Mokkhoti vā nibbānaṃ, tassa mokkhassa paṭibimbabhūtoti patimokkho. "
604947,123,845,60,71,1,113,11,Sīlasaṃvaro hi sūriyassa aruṇuggamanaṃ viya nibbānassa udayabhūto tappaṭibhāgo ca yathārahaṃ saṃkilesanibbāpanato. 
604948,123,845,72,75,1,25,3,Patimokkho eva pātimokkho. 
