605141,123,901,33,89,1,501,47,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– ete vuttappakāre kāmavitakkādike manovitakke cittassa uppilāvitahetutāya manaso uppilāve vidvā vipassanāpaññāsahitāya maggapaññāya sammadeva jānanto, tassa sahāyabhūtānaṃ sammāvāyāmasatīnaṃ atthitāya ātāpiyo satimā te ariyamaggabhāvanāya āyatiṃ uppattirahe anuggate anuppanne eva maggakkhaṇe saṃvarati, ñāṇasaṃvaravasena pidahati, āgamanapathaṃ pacchindati, evaṃbhūto ca catusaccappabodhena buddho ariyasāvako arahattādhigamena asesaṃ, anavasesaṃ ete kāmavitakkādike pajahāsi samucchindīti. "
605142,123,901,90,98,1,29,4,Etthāpi‘‘ anugate’’ tipi paṭhanti. 
