605180,123,911,2,4,1,20,2,3 . Gopālakasuttavaṇṇanā 
605181,123,912,2,28,1,123,16,"33. Tatiye {kosalesū}ti kosalā nāma jānapadino rājakumārā, tesaṃ nivāso ekopi janapado‘‘ kosalā’’ tveva vuccati, tesu kosalesu janapade. "
605182,123,912,29,36,1,59,5,Cārikaṃ {caratī}ti aturitacārikāvasena janapadacārikaṃ carati. 
605183,123,912,37,45,1,80,6,"{Mahatā}ti guṇamahattenapi mahatā, aparicchinnasaṅkhyattā saṅkhyāmahattenapi mahatā. "
605184,123,912,46,50,1,57,3,{Bhikkhusaṅghenā}ti diṭṭhisīlasāmaññasaṃhatena samaṇagaṇena. 
605185,123,912,51,54,1,16,3,Saddhin ti ekato. 
605186,123,912,55,60,1,35,4,Maggā {okkammā}ti maggato apakkamitvā. 
605187,123,912,61,70,1,111,9,Aññataraṃ rukkhamūlan ti ghanapattasākhāviṭapasampannassa sandacchāyassa mahato rukkhassa samīpasaṅkhātaṃ mūlaṃ. 
605188,123,913,2,12,1,61,8,"Aññataro {gopālako}ti eko gogaṇarakkhako, nāmena pana nando nāma. "
605189,123,913,13,35,1,170,19,"So kira aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo, yathā keṇiyo jaṭilo pabbajjāvasena, evaṃ anāthapiṇḍikassa goyūthaṃ rakkhanto gopālakattena rājapīḷaṃ apaharanto attano kuṭumbaṃ rakkhati. "
605190,123,913,36,62,1,186,22,"So kālena kālaṃ pañca gorase gahetvā, mahāseṭṭhissa santikaṃ āgantvā niyyātetvā satthu santikaṃ gantvā, satthāraṃ passati, dhammaṃ suṇāti, attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ āgamanatthāya satthāraṃ yācati. "
605191,123,913,63,96,1,252,27,"Satthā tasseva ñāṇaparipākaṃ āgamayamāno agantvā, aparabhāge mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena parivuto janapadacārikaṃ caranto,‘‘ idānissa ñāṇaṃ paripakkan’’ ti ñatvā tassa vasanaṭṭhānassa avidūre maggā okkamma aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisīdi tassa āgamanaṃ āgamayamāno. "
605192,123,913,97,127,1,195,23,"Nandopi kho‘‘ satthā kira janapadacārikaṃ caranto ito āgacchatī’’ ti sutvā, haṭṭhatuṭṭho vegena gantvā, satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā katapaṭisanthāro ekamantaṃ nisīdi, athassa bhagavā dhammaṃ desesi. "
605193,123,913,128,143,1,128,13,"So sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahitvā bhagavantaṃ nimantetvā sattāhaṃ pāyāsadānamadāsi, sattame divase bhagavā anumodanaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
605194,123,913,144,146,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
605195,123,913,147,166,1,98,13,‘‘ ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho taṃ gopālakaṃ bhagavā dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi… pe… uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmī’’ ti. 
605196,123,914,2,28,1,185,19,"Tattha {sandassesī}ti‘‘ ime dhammā kusalā, ime dhammā akusalā’’ tiādinā kusalādidhamme kammavipāke idhalokaparaloke paccakkhato dassento anupubbikathāvasāne cattāri ariyasaccāni sammā dassesi. "
605197,123,914,29,48,1,117,14,{Samādapesī}ti‘‘ saccādhigamāya ime nāma dhammā attani uppādetabbā’’ ti sīlādidhamme sammā gaṇhāpetvā tesu taṃ patiṭṭhapesi. 
605198,123,914,49,69,1,164,18,"{Samuttejesī}ti te dhammā samādinnā anukkamena bhāviyamānā nibbedhabhāgiyā hutvā tikkhavisadā yathā khippaṃ ariyamaggaṃ āvahanti, tathā sammā uttejesi sammadeva tejesi. "
605199,123,914,70,79,1,101,8,{Sampahaṃsesī}ti bhāvanāya pubbenāparaṃ visesabhāvadassanena cittassa pamodāpanavasena suṭṭhu pahaṃsesi. 
605200,123,914,80,97,1,214,14,"Apicettha sāvajjānavajjadhammesu dukkhādīsu ca sammohavinodanena sandassanaṃ, sammāpaṭipattiyaṃ pamādāpanodanena samādapanaṃ, cittassālasiyāpattivinodanena samuttejanaṃ, sammāpaṭipattisiddhiyā sampahaṃsanaṃ veditabbaṃ. "
605201,123,914,98,105,1,73,7,Evaṃ so bhagavato sāmukkaṃsikāya dhammadesanāya sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. 
605202,123,914,106,127,1,132,14,"{Adhivāsesī}ti tena diṭṭhasaccena‘‘ adhivāsetu me, bhante bhagavā’’ tiādinā nimantito kāyaṅgavācaṅgaṃ acopento citteneva adhivāsesi sādiyi. "
605203,123,914,128,135,1,24,3,Tenevāha‘‘ tuṇhībhāvenā’’ ti. 
605204,123,915,2,5,1,34,3,Appodakapāyāsan ti nirudakapāyāsaṃ. 
605205,123,915,6,10,1,35,3,{Paṭiyādāpetvā}ti sampādetvā sajjetvā. 
605206,123,915,11,20,1,80,9,Navañca sappin ti navanītaṃ gahetvā tāvadeva vilīnaṃ maṇḍasappiñca paṭiyādāpetvā. 
