605212,123,915,65,84,1,159,18,"Nīcan ti anuccaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā āsaneyeva nisīdanaṃ ariyadesavāsīnaṃ cārittaṃ, so pana satthu santike upacāravasena paññattassa dāruphalakāsanassa samīpe nisīdi. "
605213,123,915,85,95,1,69,8,Dhammiyā {kathāyā}tiādi sattame divase kataṃ anumodanaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ . 
605214,123,915,96,105,1,82,9,So kira sattāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ bhikkhusaṅghañca tattha vasāpetvā mahādānaṃ pavattesi. 
