605216,123,915,112,121,1,94,9,Satthā tassa tasmiṃ attabhāve uparimaggatthāya ñāṇaparipākābhāvato anumodanameva katvā pakkāmi. 
605217,123,916,2,9,1,47,5,"{Sīmantarikāyā}ti sīmantare, tassa gāmassa antaraṃ. "
605218,123,916,10,19,1,64,9,Gāmavāsino kira ekaṃ taḷākaṃ nissāya tena saddhiṃ kalahaṃ akaṃsu. 
605219,123,916,20,26,1,36,6,So te abhibhavitvā taṃ taḷākaṃ gaṇhi. 
605220,123,916,27,70,1,346,38,Tena baddhāghāto eko puriso taṃ satthu pattaṃ gahetvā dūraṃ anugantvā‘‘ nivattāhi upāsakā’’ ti vutte bhagavantaṃ vanditvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā bhikkhusaṅghassa ca añjaliṃ katvā yāva dassanūpacārasamatikkamā dasanakhasamodhānasamujjalaṃ añjaliṃ sirasi paggayha paṭinivattitvā dvinnaṃ gāmānaṃ antare araññappadese ekakaṃ gacchantaṃ sarena vijjhitvā māresi. 
605221,123,916,71,81,1,43,6,Tena vuttaṃ acirapakkantassa… pe… voropesī’’ ti. 
605222,123,916,82,108,1,160,21,"Kenacideva karaṇīyena ohīyitvā pacchā gacchantā bhikkhū taṃ tathā mataṃ disvā bhagavato tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ, taṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ‘‘ atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū’’ tiādi. "
605223,123,917,2,37,1,283,32,"Etamatthaṃ {viditvā}ti yasmā diṭṭhisampannaṃ ariyasāvakaṃ nandaṃ mārentena purisena ānantariyakammaṃ bahulaṃ apuññaṃ pasutaṃ, tasmā yaṃ corehi ca verīhi ca kattabbaṃ, tatopi ghorataraṃ imesaṃ sattānaṃ micchāpaṇihitaṃ cittaṃ karotīti imamatthaṃ jānitvā tadatthadīpanaṃ imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi. "
605224,123,918,2,14,1,67,10,"Tattha diso disan ti dūsako dūsanīyaṃ coro coraṃ, disvāti vacanaseso. "
605225,123,918,15,27,1,72,10,"Yaṃ taṃ {kayirā}ti yaṃ tassa anayabyasanaṃ kareyya, dutiyapadepi eseva nayo. "
605226,123,918,28,92,1,464,55,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– eko ekassa mittadubbhī coro puttadārakhettavatthugomahiṃsādīsu aparajjhanto yassa aparajjhati, tampi tatheva attani aparajjhantaṃ coraṃ disvā, verī vā pana kenacideva kāraṇena baddhaveraṃ veriṃ disvā attano kakkhaḷatāya dāruṇatāya yaṃ tassa anayabyasanaṃ kareyya, puttadāraṃ vā pīḷeyya, khettādīni vā nāseyya, jīvitā vā voropeyya , dasasu akusalakammapathesu micchāṭhapitattā micchāpaṇihitaṃ cittaṃ pāpiyo naṃ tato kare, naṃ purisaṃ pāpataraṃ tato kareyya. "
605227,123,918,93,112,1,120,18,"Vuttappakāro hi diso vā verī vā disassa vā verino vā imasmiṃyeva attabhāve dukkhaṃ vā uppādeyya, jīvitakkhayaṃ vā kareyya. "
605228,123,918,113,131,1,168,17,"Idaṃ pana akusalakammapathesu micchāṭhapitaṃ cittaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme anayabyasanaṃ pāpeti, attabhāvasatasahassesupi catūsu apāyesu khipitvā sīsamassa ukkhipituṃ na detīti. "
