605236,123,921,54,58,1,37,3,Juṇhāya {rattiyā}ti sukkapakkharattiyaṃ. 
605237,123,921,59,68,1,83,7,"Navoropitehi {kesehī}ti aciraohāritehi kesehi, itthambhūtalakkhaṇe cetaṃ karaṇavacanaṃ. "
