605364,123,946,2,14,1,75,7,36. Chaṭṭhe {piṇḍolabhāradvājo}ti piṇḍaṃ ulamāno pariyesamāno pabbajitoti piṇḍolo. 
605365,123,946,15,27,1,117,12,So kira parijiṇṇabhogo brāhmaṇo hutvā mahantaṃ bhikkhusaṅghassa lābhasakkāraṃ disvā piṇḍatthāya nikkhamitvā pabbajito. 
605366,123,946,28,49,1,112,14,"So mahantaṃ kapallaṃ‘‘ pattan’’ ti gahetvā carati, kapallapūraṃ yāguṃ pivati, bhattaṃ bhuñjati, pūvakhajjakañca khādati. "
605367,123,946,50,54,1,40,4,Athassa mahagghasabhāvaṃ satthu ārocesuṃ. 
