605369,123,946,76,86,1,89,9,"Taṃ gacchante gacchante kāle ghaṃsanena parikkhīṇaṃ, nāḷikodanamattasseva gaṇhanakaṃ jātaṃ. "
605370,123,946,87,95,1,58,7,"Tato satthu ārocesuṃ, athassa satthā pattatthavikaṃ anujāni. "
605371,123,946,96,104,1,77,8,Thero aparena samayena indriyabhāvanaṃ bhāvento aggaphale arahatte patiṭṭhāsi. 
