606420,123,1239,2,4,1,24,2,7 . Kaṅkhārevatasuttavaṇṇanā 
606421,123,1240,2,11,1,43,5,47. Sattame {kaṅkhārevato}ti tassa therassa nāmaṃ. 
606422,123,1240,12,46,1,187,22,"So hi sāsane pabbajitvā laddhūpasampado sīlavā kalyāṇadhammo viharati,‘‘ akappiyā muggā, na kappanti muggā paribhuñjituṃ, akappiyo guḷo’’ ti( mahāva.272) ca ādinā vinayakukkuccasaṅkhātakaṅkhābahulo pana hoti. "
606423,123,1240,47,51,1,31,3,Tena {kaṅkhārevato}ti paññāyittha. 
606424,123,1240,52,75,1,200,21,"So aparabhāge satthu santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā ghaṭento vāyamanto chaḷabhiññā sacchikatvā jhānasukhena phalasukhena vītināmeti, yebhuyyena pana attanā adhigataṃ ariyamaggaṃ garuṃ katvā paccavekkhati. "
606425,123,1240,76,78,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
606426,123,1240,79,87,1,49,4,‘‘ attano kaṅkhāvitaraṇavisuddhiṃ paccavekkhamāno’’ ti. 
606427,123,1240,88,163,1,339,33,"Maggapaññā hi‘‘ ahosiṃ nu kho ahaṃ atītamaddhānan’’ tiādinayapavattāya( ma. ni.1.18; saṃ. ni.2.20) soḷasavatthukāya,‘‘ buddhe kaṅkhati… pe… paṭiccasamuppannesu dhammesu kaṅkhatī’’ ti( dha. sa.1008) evaṃ vuttāya aṭṭhavatthukāya, pageva itarāsanti anavasesato sabbakaṅkhānaṃ vitaraṇato samatikkamanato, aññehi ca attanā pahātabbakilesehi accantavisujjhanato‘‘ kaṅkhāvitaraṇavisuddhī’’ ti idhādhippetā. "
606428,123,1240,164,191,1,210,22,"Tañhi ayamāyasmā dīgharattaṃ kaṅkhāpakatattā‘‘ imaṃ maggadhammaṃ adhigamma imā me kaṅkhā anavasesā pahīnā’’ ti garuṃ katvā paccavekkhamāno nisīdi, na sappaccayanāmarūpadassanaṃ aniccantikattā tassa kaṅkhāvitaraṇassa. "
606429,123,1241,2,14,1,123,11,Etamatthaṃ {viditvā}ti etaṃ ariyamaggassa anavasesakaṅkhāvitaraṇasaṅkhātaṃ atthaṃ viditvā tadatthadīpakaṃ imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi. 
606430,123,1242,2,43,1,209,31,"Tattha yā kāci kaṅkhā idha vā huraṃ {vā}ti idha imasmiṃ paccuppanne attabhāve‘‘ ahaṃ nu khosmi no nu khosmī’’ tiādinā huraṃ vā, atītānāgatesu attabhāvesu‘‘ ahosiṃ nu kho ahaṃ atītamaddhānan’’ tiādinā uppajjanakā kaṅkhā. "
606431,123,1242,44,86,1,283,35,"Sakavediyā vā paravediyā {vā}ti tā evaṃ vuttanayeneva sakaattabhāve ārammaṇavasena paṭilabhitabbāya pavattiyā sakavediyā vā parassa attabhāve paṭilabhitabbāya‘‘ buddho nu kho, no nu kho’’ tiādinā vā parasmiṃ padhāne uttame paṭilabhitabbāya pavattiyā paravediyā vā yā kāci kaṅkhā vicikicchā. "
606432,123,1242,87,118,1,323,28,"Ye jhāyino tā pajahanti sabbā, ātāpino brahmacariyaṃ {carantā}ti ye ārammaṇūpanijjhānena lakkhaṇūpanijjhānena jhāyino vipassanaṃ ussukkāpetvā catubbidhasammappadhānapāripūriyā ātāpino maggabrahmacariyaṃ carantā adhigacchantā saddhānusārīādippabhedā paṭhamamaggaṭṭhā puggalā, tā sabbā kaṅkhā pajahanti samucchindanti maggakkhaṇe. "
606433,123,1242,119,135,1,98,15,"Tato paraṃ pana tā pahīnā nāma honti, tasmā ito aññaṃ tāsaṃ accantappahānaṃ nāma natthīti adhippāyo. "
606434,123,1243,2,14,1,118,11,Iti bhagavā jhānamukhena āyasmato kaṅkhārevatassa jhānasīsena ariyamaggādhigamaṃ thomento thomanāvasena udānaṃ udānesi. 
606435,123,1243,15,45,1,124,15,"Teneva ca naṃ‘‘ etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ jhāyīnaṃ yadidaṃ kaṅkhārevato’’ ti( a. ni.1.204) jhāyībhāvena etadagge ṭhapesīti. "
