606437,123,1245,2,4,1,23,2,8 . Saṅghabhedasuttavaṇṇanā 
606438,123,1246,2,39,1,223,24,48. Aṭṭhame āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ {etadavocā}ti abhimāre payojetvā nāḷāgiriṃ vissajjāpetvā silaṃ pavaṭṭetvā bhagavato anatthaṃ kātuṃ asakkonto‘‘ saṅghaṃ bhinditvā cakkabhedaṃ karissāmī’’ ti adhippāyena etaṃ‘‘ ajjatagge’’ tiādivacanaṃ avoca. 
606439,123,1246,40,50,1,67,8,"Aññatreva {bhagavatā}ti vinā eva bhagavantaṃ, satthāraṃ akatvāti attho. "
606440,123,1246,51,57,1,47,5,Aññatra {bhikkhusaṅghā}ti vinā eva bhikkhusaṅghaṃ. 
606441,123,1246,58,78,1,178,19,Uposathaṃ karissāmi saṅghakammāni {cā}ti bhagavato ovādakārakaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ visuṃ katvā maṃ anuvattantehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ āveṇikaṃ uposathaṃ saṅghakammāni ca karissāmīti attho. 
606442,123,1246,79,95,1,139,14,Devadatto saṅghaṃ {bhindissatī}ti bhedakarānaṃ sabbesaṃ devadattena sajjitattā ekaṃseneva devadatto ajja saṅghaṃ bhindissati dvidhā karissati.
606443,123,1246,96,132,1,207,27,"‘‘ Adhammaṃ dhammo’’ tiādīsu hi aṭṭhārasasu bhedakaravatthūsu yaṃkiñci ekampi vatthuṃ dīpetvā tena tena kāraṇena‘‘ imaṃ gaṇhatha, imaṃ rocethā’’ ti saññāpetvā salākaṃ gāhetvā visuṃ saṅghakamme kate saṅgho bhinno hoti. "
606444,123,1246,133,134,1,11,1,Vuttañhetaṃ–
606445,123,1247,2,24,1,94,12,"‘ ‘ Pañcahi, upāli, ākārehi saṅgho bhijjati kammena uddesena voharanto anussāvanena salākaggāhenā’’ ti( pari.458). "
606446,123,1248,2,10,1,69,7,Tattha {kammenā}ti apalokanakammādīsu catūsu kammesu aññatarena kammena. 
606447,123,1248,11,18,1,56,5,{Uddesenā}ti pañcasu pātimokkhuddesesu aññatarena uddesena. 
606448,123,1248,19,46,1,91,9,{Voharanto}ti tāhi tāhi uppattīhi‘‘ adhammaṃ dhammo’’ tiādīni( a. ni.10.37; cūḷava.352) aṭṭhārasabhedakaravatthūni dīpento. 
606449,123,1248,47,82,1,247,28,"{Anussāvanenā}ti‘‘ nanu tumhe jānātha mayhaṃ uccākulā pabbajitabhāvaṃ bahussutabhāvañca, mādiso nāma uddhammaṃ ubbinayaṃ gāheyyāti kiṃ tumhākaṃ cittampi uppādetuṃ yuttaṃ, kimahaṃ apāyato na bhāyāmī’’ tiādinā nayena kaṇṇamūle vacībhedaṃ katvā anussāvanena. "
606450,123,1248,83,101,1,120,13,{Salākaggāhenā}ti evaṃ anussāvetvā tesaṃ cittaṃ upatthambhetvā anāvattidhamme katvā‘‘ gaṇhatha imaṃ salākan’’ ti salākaggāhena. 
606451,123,1249,2,12,1,79,9,"Ettha ca kammameva uddeso vā pamāṇaṃ, vohārānussāvanasalākaggāhā pana pubbabhāgā. "
606452,123,1249,13,24,1,119,11,Aṭṭhārasavatthudīpanavasena hi voharantena tattha rucijananatthaṃ anussāvetvā salākāya gāhitāyapi abhinnova hoti saṅgho. 
606453,123,1249,25,45,1,117,19,"Yadā panevaṃ cattāro vā atirekā vā salākaṃ gāhetvā āveṇikaṃ uddesaṃ vā kammaṃ vā karonti, tadā saṅgho bhinno nāma hoti. "
606454,123,1249,46,72,1,160,17,Devadatto ca sabbaṃ saṅghabhedassa pubbabhāgaṃ nipphādetvā‘‘ ekaṃseneva ajja āveṇikaṃ uposathaṃ saṅghakammañca karissāmī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ ajjatagge’’ tiādivacanaṃ avoca. 
606455,123,1249,73,74,1,6,1,Tenāha–
606456,123,1249,75,87,1,44,6,"‘‘ ajja, bhante, devadatto saṅghaṃ bhindissatī’’ ti. "
606457,123,1249,88,99,1,61,7,Yato avocumhā‘‘ bhedakarānaṃ sabbesaṃ devadattena sajjitattā’’ ti. 
606458,123,1250,2,15,1,150,11,Etamatthaṃ {viditvā}ti etaṃ avīcimahānirayuppattisaṃvattaniyaṃ kappaṭṭhiyaṃ atekicchaṃ devadattena nibbattiyamānaṃ saṅghabhedakammaṃ sabbākārato viditvā . 
606459,123,1250,16,28,1,147,12,Imaṃ udānan ti kusalākusalesu yathākkamaṃ sappurisāsappurisasabhāgavisabhāgapaṭipattivasena pana sukusalāti idamatthavibhāvanaṃ imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi. 
606460,123,1251,2,15,1,84,10,"Tattha sukaraṃ sādhunā {sādhū}ti attano paresañca hitaṃ sādhetīti sādhu, sammāpaṭipanno. "
606461,123,1251,16,35,1,177,19,Tena sādhunā sāriputtādinā sāvakena paccekabuddhena sammāsambuddhena aññena vā lokiyasādhunā sādhu sundaraṃ bhaddakaṃ attano paresañca hitasukhāvahaṃ sukaraṃ sukhena kātuṃ sakkā. 
606462,123,1251,36,58,1,148,21,"Sādhu pāpena dukkaran ti tadeva pana vuttalakkhaṇaṃ sādhu pāpena devadattādinā pāpapuggalena dukkaraṃ kātuṃ na sakkā, na so taṃ kātuṃ sakkotīti attho. "
606463,123,1251,59,74,1,133,15,Pāpaṃ pāpena sukaran ti pāpaṃ asundaraṃ attano paresañca anatthāvahaṃ pāpena yathāvuttapāpapuggalena sukaraṃ sukhena kātuṃ sakkuṇeyya. 
606464,123,1251,75,86,1,88,11,Pāpamariyehi dukkaran ti ariyehi pana buddhādīhi taṃ taṃ pāpaṃ dukkaraṃ durabhisambhavaṃ. 
