606467,123,1253,2,4,1,23,2,9 . Sadhāyamānasuttavaṇṇanā 
606468,123,1254,2,9,1,24,3,49. Navame {māṇavakā}ti taruṇā. 
606469,123,1254,10,15,1,51,5,Paṭhame yobbane ṭhitā brāhmaṇakumārakā idhādhippetā. 
606470,123,1255,2,8,1,58,5,{Sadhāyamānarūpā}ti uppaṇḍanajātikaṃ vacanaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ. 
606471,123,1255,9,15,1,54,5,"Aññesaṃ uppaṇḍentā sadhanti, tadatthavacanasīlāti attho. "
606472,123,1255,16,35,1,109,13,"Tassāyaṃ vacanattho– sadhanaṃ sadho, taṃ ācikkhantīti sadhayamānāti vattabbe dīghaṃ katvā‘‘ sadhāyamānā’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
606473,123,1255,36,44,1,60,8,Atha vā visesato sasedhe viya attānaṃ āvadantīti sadhāyamānā. 
606474,123,1255,45,55,1,45,6,Te evaṃ sabhāvatāya‘‘ sadhāyamānarūpā’’ ti vuttaṃ.
606475,123,1255,56,68,1,62,6,"‘‘ Saddāyamānarūpā’’ tipi pāṭho, uccāsaddamahāsaddaṃ karontāti attho. "
606476,123,1255,69,80,1,91,10,Bhagavato avidūre {atikkamantī}ti bhagavato savanavisaye taṃ taṃ mukhāruḷhaṃ vadantā atiyanti. 
606477,123,1256,2,17,1,117,12,Etamatthaṃ {viditvā}ti etaṃ tesaṃ vācāya asaññatabhāvaṃ jānitvā tadatthadīpakaṃ dhammasaṃvegavasena imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi. 
606478,123,1257,2,7,1,40,4,Tattha {parimuṭṭhā}ti dandhā muṭṭhassatino. 
606479,123,1257,8,29,1,132,15,"{Paṇḍitābhāsā}ti paṇḍitapatirūpakā‘‘ ke aññe jānanti, mayamevettha jānāmā’’ ti tasmiṃ tasmiṃ atthe attānameva jānantaṃ katvā samudācaraṇato. "
606480,123,1257,30,45,1,121,12,"{Vācāgocarabhāṇino}ti yesaṃ vācā eva gocaro visayo, te vācāgocarabhāṇino, vācāvatthumattasseva bhāṇino atthassa apariññātattā. "
606481,123,1257,46,56,1,88,10,Atha vā vācāya agocaraṃ ariyānaṃ kathāya avisayaṃ musāvādaṃ bhaṇantīti vācāgocarabhāṇino. 
606482,123,1257,57,69,1,55,8,Atha vā‘‘ gocarabhāṇino’’ ti ettha ākārassa rassabhāvo kato. 
