606490,123,1259,2,4,1,24,2,10 . Cūḷapanthakasuttavaṇṇanā 
606491,123,1260,2,24,1,161,14,50. Dasame {cūḷapanthako}ti mahāpanthakattherassa kaniṭṭhabhātikattā panthe jātattā ca daharakāle laddhavohārena aparabhāgepi ayamāyasmā‘‘ cūḷapanthako’’ tveva paññāyittha. 
606492,123,1260,25,70,1,269,26,"Guṇavisesehi pana chaḷabhiñño pabhinnapaṭisambhido‘‘ etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ manomayaṃ kāyaṃ abhinimminantānaṃ yadidaṃ cūḷapanthako, cetovivaṭṭakusalānaṃ yadidaṃ cūḷapanthako’’ ti dvīsu( a. ni.1.199) ṭhānesu bhagavatā etadagge ṭhapito asītiyā mahāsāvakesu abbhantaro. "
606493,123,1261,2,38,1,341,32,So ekadivasaṃ pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātappaṭikkanto attano divāṭṭhāne divāvihāraṃ nisinno samāpattīhi divasabhāgaṃ vītināmetvā sāyanhasamayaṃ upāsakesu dhammassavanatthaṃ anāgatesu eva vihāramajjhaṃ pavisitvā bhagavati gandhakuṭiyaṃ nisinne‘‘ akālo tāva bhagavato upaṭṭhānaṃ upasaṅkamitun’’ ti gandhakuṭipamukhe ekamantaṃ nisīdi pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā. 
606494,123,1261,39,41,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
606495,123,1261,42,65,1,147,19,‘‘ tena kho pana samayena āyasmā cūḷapanthako bhagavato avidūre nisinno hoti pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā’’ ti. 
606496,123,1261,66,74,1,63,8,So hi tadā kālaparicchedaṃ katvā samāpattiṃ samāpajjitvā nisīdi. 
606497,123,1262,2,12,1,106,9,Etamatthaṃ {viditvā}ti etaṃ āyasmato cūḷapanthakassa kāyacittānaṃ sammāpaṇihitabhāvasaṅkhātaṃ atthaṃ jānitvā. 
606498,123,1262,13,33,1,192,19,"Imaṃ udānan ti aññopi yo passaddhakāyo sabbiriyāpathesu upaṭṭhitassati samāhito, tassa bhikkhuno anupādā parinibbānapariyosānassa visesādhigamassa tattha pātubhāvavibhāvanaṃ imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi. "
606499,123,1263,2,35,1,354,30,"Tattha ṭhitena {kāyenā}ti kāyadvārikassa asaṃvarassa pahānena akaraṇena sammā ṭhapitena copanakāyena, tathā cakkhādīnaṃ indriyānaṃ nibbisevanabhāvakaraṇena suṭṭhu ṭhapitena pañcadvārikakāyena, saṃyatahatthapādatāya hatthakukkuccādīnaṃ abhāvato apariphandanena ṭhitena karajakāyena cāti saṅkhepato sabbenapi kāyena nibbikāratāsaṅkhātena niccalabhāvena ṭhitena. "
606500,123,1263,36,39,1,31,3,Etenassa sīlapārisuddhi dassitā. 
606501,123,1263,40,44,1,41,4,Itthambhūtalakkhaṇe ca idaṃ karaṇavacanaṃ. 
606502,123,1263,45,52,1,67,6,Ṭhitena {cetasā}ti cittassa ṭhitiparidīpanena samādhisampadaṃ dasseti. 
606503,123,1263,53,61,1,36,6,Samādhi hi cittassa‘ ṭhitī’ ti vuccati. 
606504,123,1263,62,77,1,121,14,"Tasmā samathavasena vipassanāvaseneva vā ekaggatāya sati cittaṃ ārammaṇe ekodibhāvūpagamanena ṭhitaṃ nāma hoti, na aññathā. "
606505,123,1263,78,90,1,116,12,Idañca yathāvuttakāyacittānaṃ ṭhapanaṃ samādahanaṃ sabbasmiṃ kāle sabbesu ca iriyāpathesu icchitabbanti dassento āha–
606506,123,1263,91,102,1,32,6,‘‘ tiṭṭhaṃ nisinno uda vā sayāno’’ ti . 
606507,123,1263,103,108,1,27,4,Tattha vā -saddo aniyamattho. 
