606801,123,1322,34,63,1,128,16,"Sassatādivaseneva khamanaṃ khanti, rocanaṃ ruci, atthato‘‘ sassato attā ca loko cā’’ tiādinā( udā.55) pavatto cittavipallāso saññāvipallāso ca. "
