607070,123,1370,75,80,1,52,4,Telappadīpesu {jhāyamānesū}ti telapajjotesu jalamānesu. 
607071,123,1371,2,36,1,385,32,"Nanu ca bhagavato byāmappabhā pakatiyā byāmamattappadesaṃ abhibyāpetvā candimasūriyālokaṃ abhibhavitvā ghanabahalaṃ buddhālokaṃ vissajjentī andhakāraṃ vidhamitvā tiṭṭhati, kāyappabhāpi nīlapītādivasena chabbaṇṇaghanabuddharasmiyo vissajjetvā pakatiyāva samantato asītihatthappadesaṃ obhāsentī tiṭṭhati, evaṃ buddhālokeneva ekobhāsabhūte bhagavato nisinnokāse padīpakaraṇe kiccaṃ natthīti? "
607072,123,1371,37,50,1,123,12,"Saccaṃ natthi, tathāpi puññatthikā upāsakā bhagavato bhikkhusaṅghassa ca pūjākaraṇatthaṃ devasikaṃ telappadīpaṃ upaṭṭhapenti. "
