607125,123,1386,2,4,1,9,2,7 . Cūḷavaggo
607126,123,1387,2,4,1,36,2,1 . Paṭhamalakuṇḍakabhaddiyasuttavaṇṇanā 
607127,123,1388,2,30,1,138,16,"61. Cūḷavaggassa paṭhame lakuṇḍakabhaddiyan ti ettha {bhaddiyo}ti tassa āyasmato nāmaṃ, kāyassa pana rassattā‘‘ lakuṇḍakabhaddiyo’’ ti naṃ sañjānanti. "
607128,123,1388,31,42,1,97,11,So kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto mahaddhano mahābhogo rūpena apāsādiko dubbaṇṇo duddasiko okoṭimako. 
607129,123,1388,43,66,1,224,23,So ekadivasaṃ satthari jetavane viharante upāsakehi saddhiṃ vihāraṃ gantvā dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā laddhūpasampado satthu santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto sotāpattiphalaṃ pāpuṇi. 
607130,123,1388,67,83,1,143,14,"Tadā sekkhā bhikkhū yebhuyyena āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ upasaṅkamitvā uparimaggatthāya kammaṭṭhānaṃ yācanti, dhammadesanaṃ yācanti, pañhaṃ pucchanti. "
607131,123,1388,84,96,1,83,10,"So tesaṃ adhippāyaṃ pūrento kammaṭṭhānaṃ ācikkhati, dhammaṃ deseti, pañhaṃ vissajjeti. "
607132,123,1388,97,120,1,181,18,"Te ghaṭentā vāyamantā appekacce sakadāgāmiphalaṃ, appekacce anāgāmiphalaṃ, appekacce arahattaṃ, appekacce tisso vijjā, appekacce chaḷabhiññā, appekacce catasso paṭisambhidā adhigacchanti. "
