607367,123,1444,2,34,1,293,30,"Tattha yassa siyā sabbadā sati, satataṃ kāyagatā {upaṭṭhitā}ti yassa āraddhavipassakassa ekadivasaṃ cha koṭṭhāse katvā sabbasmimpi kāle nāmarūpabhedena duvidhepi kāye gatā kāyārammaṇā pañcannaṃ upādānakkhandhānaṃ aniccādisammasanavasena satataṃ nirantaraṃ sātaccābhiyogavasena sati upaṭṭhitā siyā. "
