607372,123,1446,11,41,1,173,28,"Tesu pubbabhāgavasena tāva no cassa no ca me {siyā}ti atītakāle mama kilesakammaṃ no cassa na bhaveyya ce, imasmiṃ paccuppannakāle ayaṃ attabhāvo no ca me siyā na me uppajjeyya. "
