607377,123,1447,55,104,1,319,45,"Na {bhavissatī}ti attani attaniye bhavitabbaṃ yathā cidaṃ nāmarūpaṃ etarahi ca atīte ca attattaniyaṃ suññaṃ, evaṃ na bhavissati na me bhavissati, anāgatepi khandhavinimutto attā nāma na koci na me bhavissati na pavattissati, tato eva kiñci palibodhaṭṭhāniyaṃ na me bhavissati āyatimpi attaniyaṃ nāma na me kiñci bhavissatīti. "
