607533,123,1486,28,35,1,47,6,{Samādapetī}ti tameva atthaṃ te bhikkhū gaṇhāpeti. 
607534,123,1486,36,43,1,58,6,{Samuttejetī}ti tadatthagahaṇe ussāhaṃ janento tejeti joteti. 
607535,123,1486,44,50,1,60,5,{Sampahaṃsetī}ti nibbānaguṇehi sammadeva sabbappakārehi toseti. 
607536,123,1487,2,44,1,185,20,Atha vā {sandassetī}ti‘‘ so sabbasaṅkhārasamatho sabbūpadhipaṭinissaggā taṇhakkhayo virāgo nirodho’’ tiādinā( ma. ni.1.281;2.337; mahāva.8) nayeneva sabbathā tena tena pariyāyena tesaṃ tesaṃ ajjhāsayānurūpaṃ sammā dasseti. 
607537,123,1487,45,65,1,144,15,{Samādapetī}ti‘‘ iminā ariyamaggena taṃ adhigantabban’’ ti adhigamapaṭipadāya saddhiṃ tattha bhikkhū ninnapoṇapabbhāre karonto sammā ādapeti gaṇhāpeti. 
607538,123,1487,66,99,1,279,25,"{Samuttejetī}ti etaṃ dukkaraṃ durabhisambhavanti‘‘ mā sammāpaṭipattiyaṃ pamādaṃ antarāvosānaṃ āpajjatha, upanissayasampannassa vīriyavato nayidaṃ dukkaraṃ, tasmā sīlavisuddhiādivisuddhipaṭipadāya uṭṭhahatha ghaṭayatha vāyameyyāthā’’ ti nibbānādhigamāya ussāheti, tattha vā cittaṃ vodapeti. "
