608149,123,1645,78,85,1,68,7,Tassa pabbajjāsamaye dinnaovādena bhavattayaṃ ādittaṃ viya upaṭṭhāsi. 
608150,123,1645,86,92,1,55,6,So vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā khuraggeyeva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
