608210,123,1659,2,52,1,402,42,"80. Dasame tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū {āmantesī}ti bhagavā rājagahe yathābhirantaṃ viharitvā janapadacārikaṃ caranto anukkamena sāvatthiṃ patvā jetavane viharantoyeva yesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ āyasmato dabbassa mallaputtassa parinibbānaṃ apaccakkhaṃ, tesaṃ taṃ paccakkhaṃ katvā dassetuṃ, yepi ca mettiyabhūmajakehi katena abhūtena abbhācikkhaṇena there gāravarahitā puthujjanā, tesaṃ there bahumānuppādanatthañca āmantesi. "
