608689,124,140,20,52,1,334,28,"Yasmā ca so bhagavato vacanassa atthabyañjanappabhedaparicchedavasena sakalasāsanasampatiogāhanena niravasesaparahitapāripūrikāraṇabhūto evaṃbhaddako ākāro na sammā appaṇihitattano pubbe akatapuññassa vā hoti, tasmā {itī}ti iminā bhaddakena ākārena pacchimacakkadvayasampattimattano dīpeti, sutan ti savanayogena purimacakkadvayasampattiṃ. "
