608699,124,141,2,15,1,128,10,Aparo nayo– {itī}ti iminā pubbe vuttanayena nānappakārappaṭivedhadīpakena attano atthapaṭibhānapaṭisambhidāsampattisabbhāvaṃ dīpeti. 
