609248,124,285,72,76,1,47,3,Kiñca nīvaraṇasaṃyojanappadhānassa dassanatthaṃ. 
609249,124,285,77,96,1,178,18,"Yathā hi nīvaraṇabhāvena avijjā saṃkilesadhammānaṃ padhānabhūtā pubbaṅgamā ca, evaṃ saṃyojanabhāvena nesaṃ taṇhāti tadadhīnappadhānabhāvaṃ dassetuṃ suttadvaye evamete dhammā vuttā. "
609250,124,285,97,121,1,119,14,"Apica visesena avijjā nibbānasukhaṃ nivāretīti ‘‘ nīvaraṇan’’ ti vuttā, taṇhā saṃsāradukkhena satte saṃyojetīti‘‘ saṃyojanan’’ ti. "
