609330,124,303,104,147,1,269,27,"So tesaṃ paccayānañca paccayuppannānañca yāthāvasarasalakkhaṇaṃ vavatthapetvā‘‘ ime dhammā ahutvā bhavanti, hutvā nirujjhanti, tasmā aniccā’’ ti aniccalakkhaṇaṃ āropeti,‘‘ udayabbayapaṭipīḷitattā dukkhā’’ ti dukkhalakkhaṇaṃ āropeti,‘‘ avasavattanato anattā’’ ti anattalakkhaṇaṃ āropeti. "
